Belle Bennett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Belle_Bennett 0 Belle Bennett (April 22, 1891 – November 4, 1932) was a stage and screen actress who started her professional career in vaudeville. She was born in Milaca, Minnesota. Belle_Bennett ( April_22_,_1891 – November_4_,_1932 ) was a_stage_and_screen_actress who started her_professional_career in vaudeville .
